items.name: forge
items.description: Forge is a self-hosted middleware that unifies access to multiple AI model providers (like OpenAI, Anthropic) via a single API. It supports OpenAI-compatible interfaces, encrypted API key management, and easy integration into existing tools and frontends. Built for security, scalability, and extensibility.
